    examTip: "Focus on the chronological order of incident response phases; preparation always comes first.",
    memoryAid: "P-D-C-E-R-L: People Don't Cause Errors, Really Likely (Preparation, Detection, Containment, Eradication, Recovery, Lessons Learned)",
    reference: "NIST Incident Response Framework",
