    options: ["Only FDA regulations","SOX (financial reporting controls), PCI DSS (payment card data), GDPR/CCPA (privacy), HIPAA (healthcare data), and SOC reporting standards — each imposing specific IT control requirements","Only building fire codes","Only environmental regulations"],
