    educational: "IT compliance is crucial for organizations handling sensitive data, especially financial information. These frameworks ensure data integrity, security, and privacy, protecting both the organization and its stakeholders. Understanding these frameworks is essential for maintaining trust and avoiding legal repercussions.",
