      2: "Why option C is WRONG - While automated reconciliation tools may generate reports, including PDFs, this is only one aspect of their functionality; they offer a comprehensive suite of features beyond simple reporting.",
      3: "Why option D is WRONG - Automated reconciliation tools are designed to identify and highlight discrepancies, not hide them; hiding discrepancies would defeat the purpose of reconciliation and weaken internal controls.",
