    examTip: "When a question emphasizes 'throughout the data lifecycle' or 'multiple points of vulnerability,' think about comprehensive solutions like encryption at rest and in transit.",
    memoryAid: "Think of 'R&T' - Rest and Transit - for comprehensive encryption coverage.",
