      2: "Why option C is WRONG - Software development is typically handled by a development team, not a SOC, which focuses on security monitoring and incident response.",
      3: "Why option D is WRONG - Help desk support addresses general IT issues, while a SOC specializes in identifying and responding to security threats and vulnerabilities.",
