      2: "Why option C is WRONG - Audit opinions require professional judgment and consideration of various factors, which cannot be automated by predictive analytics alone.",
      3: "Why option D is WRONG - Predictive analytics is primarily used for audit procedures related to financial statement accuracy, not for complying with tax filing requirements.",
