    question: "How does the COSO Internal Control Framework relate to IT controls?",
    options: ["COSO has no relevance to IT controls","Principle 11 of COSO 2013 specifically addresses controls over technology, requiring that management selects and develops general IT controls to support the achievement of objectives","COSO only applies to manufacturing companies","COSO replaced all IT-specific frameworks"],
