      2: "Why option C is WRONG - Empty space only describes a cold site, which requires significant setup and data restoration before it can be used for business continuity.",
      3: "Why option D is WRONG - Basic infrastructure without data describes a warm site. While it has the necessary hardware, it lacks the crucial current data needed for immediate operation.",
