    examTip: "On the exam, remember that a good DR plan involves a *range* of testing methods, not just one or none.",
    memoryAid: "Think of DR testing as a 'Ladder of Assurance': Documentation -> Tabletop -> Walkthrough -> Simulation -> Parallel -> Full Interruption. Each step builds more confidence.",
