    options: ["Only whether the ransom payment was properly recorded as an expense","Data integrity — whether any financial data was modified, deleted, or corrupted during the attack, and whether the restored data can be relied upon for financial reporting purposes","Only the adequacy of cyber insurance coverage","The attack is not relevant to the financial audit if operations have resumed"],
