    examTip: "When you see PKI on the exam, immediately think of digital certificates and the roles of the Certificate Authority and Registration Authority.",
    memoryAid: "CA-RA-Cert-Key: Certificate Authority, Registration Authority, Certificates, Keys - the core of PKI.",
