    examTip: "Pay close attention to units of time (minutes, hours, days) when evaluating RTO and RPO. Also, consider that the question is asking for the 'BEST' option, implying a trade-off between cost and functionality.",
    memoryAid: "RTO = Time; RPO = Data. Think of 'T' in RTO as 'Time' and 'P' in RPO as 'Point' in time, which relates to data.",
    reference: "NIST Cybersecurity Framework, COBIT",
