    options: ["Allow all inbound traffic from any source to 192.168.1.100 on any port.","Allow inbound traffic from the internet to the firewall's external IP address on TCP port 80, forwarding it to 192.168.1.100:8080.","Allow inbound traffic from the internet to the firewall's external IP address on TCP port 8080, forwarding it to 192.168.1.100:8080.","Allow outbound traffic from 192.168.1.100 to the internet on TCP port 8080."],
