    options: ["Immediately disconnect the 5 affected workstations from the network and begin forensic analysis.","Run a full system scan on all workstations using the existing antivirus software and monitor for further detections.","Notify all clients that their data may have been compromised and offer free credit monitoring.","Contact the antivirus software vendor to report the incident and request an updated virus definition."],
