    examTip: "Always pay close attention to the period covered by the SOC 1 report and compare it to the user entity's reporting period. If there's a gap, remember the need for a gap analysis and consideration of complementary user entity controls (CUECs).",
    memoryAid: "GAP: Gate, Analyze, Perform (gap analysis, analyze CUECs, perform testing).",
