    section: "ISC",
    blueprintArea: "ISC-I",
    topic: "Cloud computing models (IaaS, PaaS, SaaS)",
    subtopic: "Choosing the right cloud service model",
    difficulty: "medium",
    skillLevel: "Analysis",
    question: "XYZ Corporation, a rapidly growing software development company, needs to migrate its development and testing environments to the cloud. They want to retain maximum control over the operating systems, servers, and networking components, while minimizing the need to manage the physical hardware. They also want a scalable solution for deploying and managing their applications. Which cloud service model is MOST suitable for XYZ Corporation's needs?",
