    options: ["A. Defer addressing the vulnerability until the next sprint to avoid delaying the current sprint's goals.","B. Immediately halt all other development activities to address the vulnerability within the current sprint, even if it means extending the sprint deadline.","C. Document the vulnerability and prioritize it for remediation in the next sprint, while implementing a temporary compensating control to mitigate the immediate risk.","D. Implement the quickest and easiest fix available, regardless of its long-term effectiveness, to maintain the sprint schedule."],
