    options: ["A. Implementing strong encryption (e.g., TLS 1.2 or higher) for all API communication and using OAuth 2.0 for authentication and authorization.","B. Regularly scanning the CRM system for vulnerabilities and patching them promptly, regardless of API security measures.","C. Requiring all employees to change their passwords every 30 days and complete annual security awareness training.","D. Implementing a strict data retention policy for the on-premise CRM system, deleting client data after three years to minimize risk."],
