    options: ["Conduct a gap analysis between the IT implementation plan and the company's strategic objectives, focusing on key performance indicators (KPIs) and benefits realization.","Prioritize the immediate deployment of the ERP system across all departments to minimize disruption and maximize user adoption.","Implement a robust cybersecurity framework, such as NIST Cybersecurity Framework, to protect sensitive data within the new ERP system.","Focus on optimizing the technical performance of the ERP system, including server capacity and network bandwidth, to ensure system stability."],
