    options: ["Implement a mandatory training program for all employees on the new ERP system's basic functionality.","Roll back all unauthorized configuration changes immediately to the original default settings of the ERP system.","Conduct a thorough investigation to identify the unauthorized changes, assess their impact on financial reporting, and implement stronger change control procedures.","Purchase additional cybersecurity software to monitor and prevent future unauthorized access to the ERP system."],
