    options: ["Online Banking: RTO = 6 hours, RPO = 2 hours; ATM Network: RTO = 10 hours, RPO = 4 hours; Check Processing: RTO = 30 hours, RPO = 12 hours; Loan Origination: RTO = 96 hours, RPO = 24 hours","Online Banking: RTO = 3 hours, RPO = 1 hour; ATM Network: RTO = 6 hours, RPO = 2 hours; Check Processing: RTO = 18 hours, RPO = 6 hours; Loan Origination: RTO = 48 hours, RPO = 12 hours","Online Banking: RTO = 4 hours, RPO = 0 hours; ATM Network: RTO = 8 hours, RPO = 0 hours; Check Processing: RTO = 24 hours, RPO = 0 hours; Loan Origination: RTO = 72 hours, RPO = 0 hours","Online Banking: RTO = 2 hours, RPO = 4 hours; ATM Network: RTO = 4 hours, RPO = 8 hours; Check Processing: RTO = 12 hours, RPO = 24 hours; Loan Origination: RTO = 36 hours, RPO = 72 hours"],
