    options: ["Yes, the solution meets both the RTO and RPO requirements.","No, the solution meets the RTO requirement but not the RPO requirement.","No, the solution meets the RPO requirement but not the RTO requirement.","No, the solution meets neither the RTO nor the RPO requirement."],
