    options: ["A. Implementing a cold site with daily tape backups. The backups are stored offsite and can be restored within 24 hours.","B. Implementing a warm site with weekly data replication. A full system restoration can be completed within 8 hours.","C. Implementing a hot site with continuous data replication and automated failover capabilities. System failover is estimated to take 15 minutes.","D. Implementing a cloud-based backup solution with hourly snapshot backups. A full system restoration to the cloud is estimated to take 6 hours."],
