    question: "XYZ Company, a rapidly growing fintech startup, needs to deploy a new customer-facing application with high availability and scalability. They have limited in-house IT infrastructure expertise. After evaluating different cloud service models, they opted for a Platform as a Service (PaaS) solution. According to industry best practices like COBIT and NIST Cybersecurity Framework, which of the following responsibilities MOST likely falls on XYZ Company?",
    options: ["Maintaining the physical security of the data center hosting the PaaS infrastructure.","Managing the operating system and underlying virtual machines supporting the PaaS environment.","Developing, deploying, and managing the application code and data within the PaaS environment.","Ensuring network security at the infrastructure level, including firewall configuration and intrusion detection."],
