    educational: "Cloud computing offers different service models: IaaS (Infrastructure as a Service), PaaS (Platform as a Service), and SaaS (Software as a Service). Each model has a different allocation of responsibilities between the cloud provider and the customer. Understanding this shared responsibility model is crucial for effective risk management and security in cloud environments.",
    examTip: "Focus on the specific responsibilities that are shifted to the cloud provider in each model (IaaS, PaaS, SaaS). Pay close attention to keywords like 'physical infrastructure,' 'operating system,' 'application code,' and 'data' when analyzing cloud-related questions.",
