    options: ["Implement multi-factor authentication for all users accessing the patient portal, regardless of their role.","Immediately disable the API and implement robust authentication and authorization controls before re-enabling it.","Conduct a penetration test of the entire EHR system to identify other potential vulnerabilities.","Inform all patients about the potential data breach and offer free credit monitoring services."],
