    explanation: "Disabling the API and implementing robust authentication and authorization controls is the most critical immediate action. This directly addresses the identified vulnerability and prevents potential unauthorized access and modification of sensitive patient data. NIST CSF and ISO 27001 emphasize the importance of access controls and data protection. This option directly remediates the immediate risk.",
