    options: ["Infrastructure as a Service (IaaS); XYZ is responsible for securing the operating system, applications, data, runtime, middleware, and virtualisation layers.","Platform as a Service (PaaS); XYZ is responsible for securing the applications and data only.","Software as a Service (SaaS); The cloud provider is responsible for securing all layers, including the applications and data.","Function as a Service (FaaS); XYZ is only responsible for securing the function code and data ingested into the function."],
