    question: "A company implements a new Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP) system. To ensure consistent and secure operations, what is the MOST important initial step in configuration management?",
    options: ["Establishing a baseline configuration for all ERP system components.","Providing end-user training on the ERP system's functionality.","Immediately applying all available security patches to the ERP system.","Creating a disaster recovery plan for the ERP system."],
