      3: "Data center consolidation focuses primarily on cost reduction, which is a valid IT objective but not directly linked to the stated business goals of increasing market share and customer satisfaction. While cost reduction *could* indirectly benefit these goals, the CRM solution is a more direct and demonstrable link.",
