    options: ["Click the link and update her information to ensure compliance and avoid penalties.","Forward the email to the IRS using the email address provided in the email to verify its authenticity.","Independently navigate to the official IRS website (irs.gov) and check her account status or contact the IRS directly through a known phone number.","Reply to the email asking for more information and clarification about the flagged tax return."],
