    options: ["ABC Corp must erase the personal data immediately without exception.","ABC Corp must erase the personal data unless it has a legitimate overriding interest, such as compliance with a legal obligation under US law, in retaining the data.","ABC Corp must only erase the personal data if the citizen pays a processing fee of $50 to cover administrative costs.","ABC Corp can ignore the request as GDPR only applies to companies physically located in the EU."],
