    examTip: "Pay close attention to the wording of GDPR-related questions. Recognize keywords like 'legitimate interest,' 'legal obligation,' and 'necessary' as they often indicate the correct answer involves an exception to a general rule.",
    memoryAid: "Remember 'ERASE': Erasure, Rectification, Access, Specify, Exceptions. This can help recall the key rights and the fact that exceptions often exist.",
