    options: ["Notify all clients, regardless of residency, of the potential data breach to maintain transparency and avoid potential reputational damage.","Conduct a detailed assessment to determine the scope of the data breach, identify affected individuals and the type of data compromised, and then determine applicable reporting requirements under GDPR and CCPA.","Immediately file a claim with their cyber insurance provider to cover the recovery costs and delegate the responsibility of determining reporting requirements to the insurance company.","Contact local law enforcement to report the ransomware attack and allow them to take control of the investigation to ensure proper handling of the incident."],
