    options: ["Maintain a constant temperature of 85°F (29°C) and humidity level of 70% to minimize energy consumption.","Install a basic HVAC system with temperature monitoring only, and rely on local weather forecasts for humidity management.","Implement a redundant HVAC system with precise temperature and humidity controls, setting the temperature between 68°F (20°C) and 72°F (22°C) and humidity between 40% and 60%, along with continuous monitoring and alerts.","Focus primarily on fire suppression systems and neglect humidity controls, assuming hardware is inherently resistant to moisture damage."],
