    educational: "Environmental controls in server rooms are crucial for maintaining the longevity and reliability of hardware. High temperatures can cause overheating and component failure, while excessive humidity can lead to corrosion. Monitoring and alerts are vital for timely intervention to prevent damage and data loss.",
