    options: ["The EDR system lacked real-time threat intelligence updates, relying on outdated signature databases.","The EDR system's behavioral analysis component was configured with overly strict thresholds, causing frequent false positives and desensitizing users to alerts.","The EDR system was properly configured, but the firm's incident response plan was inadequate in containing the ransomware's lateral movement.","The EDR system was not integrated with the firm's Security Information and Event Management (SIEM) system, hindering centralized monitoring and analysis."],
