    options: ["Revoke John Doe's certificate and distribute the updated Certificate Revocation List (CRL).","Immediately reissue all certificates to all employees to prevent further fraudulent transactions.","Change the company's root certificate authority (CA) private key.","Inform all customers of the potential compromise and advise them to change their passwords."],
