    options: ["SMS messages are susceptible to interception, SIM swapping, and other attacks, potentially compromising the second factor.","SMS-based OTP is not compliant with GDPR and CCPA regulations, potentially leading to fines and penalties.","SMS messages are easily lost or delayed, leading to frustration and reduced productivity for employees.","SMS-based OTP requires significant infrastructure investment and ongoing maintenance costs, making it an expensive solution."],
