    question: "Under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), which of the following rights is a data subject entitled to exercise?",
    options: ["The right to demand a full refund for any product purchased from a company processing their data.","The right to obtain from the controller confirmation as to whether or not personal data concerning him or her are being processed, and, where that is the case, access to the personal data.","The right to determine the pricing of their personal data when sold to third parties.","The right to completely erase all publicly available information about them from the internet, regardless of source."],
