    options: ["It automatically identifies and quarantines all newly discovered malware based on signature analysis.","It allows only pre-approved applications to run on the firm's systems, preventing the execution of unauthorized software.","It proactively scans all incoming and outgoing network traffic for malicious code, blocking potential threats at the perimeter.","It provides real-time monitoring of system processes, detecting and terminating suspicious activities based on behavioral analysis."],
