    options: ["SMS-based codes, as they are readily available and require minimal user training.","Authenticator apps using Time-based One-Time Password (TOTP), coupled with employee training on identifying phishing attempts.","Hardware security keys, as they provide strong resistance to phishing and meet compliance requirements for strong authentication.","A combination of SMS-based codes for initial setup and authenticator apps for daily use, balancing security and user convenience."],
