    options: ["Immediately recalibrate all temperature and humidity sensors within the data center and implement a quarterly calibration schedule.","Conduct a full risk assessment focusing solely on the potential impact of uncalibrated sensors on data integrity and system availability.","Implement a redundant data backup system to mitigate potential data loss due to equipment failure caused by temperature fluctuations.","Report the uncalibrated sensors to the firm's errors and omissions (E&O) insurance provider and await their guidance on remediation."],
