    question: "A CPA firm, Smith & Jones, recently completed a penetration test of its client portal, which allows clients to upload sensitive financial documents. The penetration test report identified several vulnerabilities, including weak password policies and an unpatched server component. Which of the following actions is the MOST appropriate NEXT step for Smith & Jones to take?",
